ing multiplayer .io game about gathering resources and building a base alone or with your friends.',1,NULL,0,0,7,'Doomz.io.png',0,'https://www.doomz.io/'),(163,'https://junon.io/',0,'Junon.io is a co-op Space-Station Building Game. You are stranded in an asteroid, and you need food, oxygen, stamina in order to survive. You have to work with other players in gathering various resources (ores,fuel,water,oxygen,power), but you can also hire bots/slaves to do tasks for you (cleaning dirty floors, butchering corpses, farming, harvesting, turret ammo refill). Additionally, the enemy will send raids every 3 days so you have to ensure that proper defenses are setup in order to survive.',1,NULL,0,0,7,'Junon.io.png',0,'https://junon.io/'),(164,'https://asdf.games/sharks3d/',0,'Sharks 3D Multiplayer is a free IOGame. Welcome to the wild and wonderful world of Sharks! A 3D game where you grow by eating smaller sharks, the tails of larger sharks, or dead sharks.',1,NULL,0,0,6,'Sharks 3D Multiplayer.png',0,'https://asdf.games/sharks3d/'),(165,'https://fisp.io/',0,'Fisp.space is a free iogame. This is the ultimate candy-colored arena.  There are glowing orbs of pure energy sprinkled all over the map and all you have to do is collect as many as you can in order to grow big and devastate your opponents. This game is all about being the biggest fidget spinner in the world. You become the biggest fidget spinner by slowly consuming the candy-colored orbs, but beware! The arena is full of enemies who wish to smash into you and steal your orb energy. If enough of them hit you and do it hard enough you\'ll lose all of your candy-colored orbs and be ejected from the arena in shame. Can you collect, grow and dominate or are you fated to be the runt of the litter. The choice is yours and it is a choice you can forge through your iron will.',1,NULL,0,0,6,'Fisp.space.png',0,'https://fisp.io/'),(166,'https://yohoho.io',0,'Mouse: Controls movement',1,NULL,0,0,7,'YoHoHo.io.png',0,'https://yohoho.